    HomeScreen is responsible for navigation to the other .

    Class responsible for the Map Page.

    Model is a singleton class that holds information such as the current user and events.

    RecyclerViewAdapter is necessary for RecyclerView to put the values of the events into the cards.
    RecyclerViewTest
    Example local unit test, which will execute on the development machine (host).
    UserRecyclerViewAdapter
    UserRecyclerViewAdapter is the same as the first, but for the events that the user specifically signed up for.
